---
// Sustainability.astro
// Section id: #sustainability
// JS binds to: #sustainability-hero, #sustainability-hero-inner,
// #sustainability-tagline, #sustainability-title, #sustainability-title-pre,
// #sustainability-title-main, #sustainability-desc,
// #sustainability-items, .sustainability-item, .sustainability-item-num,
// #sustainability-rive-canvas-harvesting, #sustainability-rive-canvas-text.
// All ids, classes, and data-* attributes are preserved verbatim.
---

<div id="sustainability" class="section">
  <div class="section__inner o-container">

    <!-- Hero text block -->
    <div id="sustainability-hero">
      <div id="sustainability-hero-inner">
        <div id="sustainability-tagline" class="sub2">100% open-source mindset</div>
        <div id="sustainability-title">
          <h4 id="sustainability-title-pre">Always building,</h4>
          <h2 id="sustainability-title-main">hardik verma</h2>
        </div>
        <div id="sustainability-desc" class="body2">
          Built from late-night side projects, <br />open-source contributions, and a stubborn refusal
          <br />to ship something I don't fully understand.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Three stat items -->
    <div id="sustainability-items" class="o-grid">

      <!-- Item 1: WAM -->
      <div class="sustainability-item">
        <h3 class="sustainability-item-title">University <br />WAM at <br />UNSW</h3>
        <div class="sustainability-item-desc body2">
          Bachelor of Engineering (Software) (Honours) at UNSW, currently in 3rd year. Top of cohort for several courses.
        </div>
        <div class="sustainability-item-num">82</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 2: project cadence - Rive animation canvas -->
      <div class="sustainability-item">
        <h4 class="sustainability-item-title">Time from <br />idea to demo</h4>
        <div class="sustainability-item-desc body2">
          Most of my projects ship a working prototype within weeks. Small, fast feedback loops are the whole game.
        </div>
        <canvas id="sustainability-rive-canvas-harvesting"></canvas>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 3: ego - Rive animation canvas -->
      <div class="sustainability-item">
        <h4 class="sustainability-item-title">Ego draw <br />while pairing</h4>
        <div class="sustainability-item-desc body2">
          Zero. Strong opinions, loosely held. I'd rather ship the right idea than win the argument.
        </div>
        <canvas id="sustainability-rive-canvas-text"></canvas>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</div>